HEADWORD: Corollaceous
<hw>Cor`ol*la"ceous</hw> <pr>(k?r`?l-l?"sh?s)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Pertaining to, or resembling, a corolla; having the form or texture
of a corolla.</def>⟦br⟧
